images.caption: Lib Dems GAIN seat from Labour

leaflet.additionalNotes: The by-election saw Labour's vote collapse, signalling a collapse in support ahead of the all-important General Election. The Lib Dems have campaigned vigorously, flooding the area with high profile figures and now have delivered constituents' request to 'Open up Cambridge Lakes'.
